  ],
  "remarks": "Vladimir Medvedev is the Director of JSC GosNIIP (a.k.a. State Scientific Research Institute Of Instrument Making). JSC GosNIIP is a Russian military-industrial state enterprise that develops, inter alia, control systems for anti-submarine and cruise missiles deployed by the Russian Armed Forces. Moreover, JSC GosNIIP is a subsidiary of the Joint Stock Company Almaz-Antey air and space defence corporation, a Russian state-owned arms manufacturer that develops anti-aircraft weaponry and cruise missile systems for the Russian military.",
